### 1. Auth - Register new client
# @name register
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test Client"
}

###

### 2. Auth - Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Capture Token
@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### 3. Get Current User Profile (Requires Token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get Categories (Public)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/categories

###

### 5. Get Featured Freelancers (Public)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/freelancers/featured

###

### 6. Create a Project (Requires Token)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Создать MVP платформы",
  "description": "Нужен фуллстек разработчик на React и NestJS",
  "budget": 500000,
  "budgetType": "FIXED",
  "categoryId": "replace-with-category-id-from-step-4",
  "skills": ["React", "NestJS"]
}

###

### 7. AI - Enhance Project
POST http://localhost:3001/api/ai/enhance-project
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "надо сделать сайт кафе",
  "description": "сделать простое меню и корзину"
}
